I. Adding the riotboard layer to your build
=================================================

--- replace with specific instructions for the riotboard layer ---

In order to use this layer, you need to make the build system aware of
it.

Assuming the riotboard layer exists at the top-level of your
yocto build tree, you can add it to the build system by adding the
location of the riotboard layer to bblayers.conf, along with any
other layers needed. e.g.:

  BBLAYERS ?= " \
    /path/to/yocto/meta \
    /path/to/yocto/meta-poky \
    /path/to/yocto/meta-yocto-bsp \
    /path/to/yocto/meta-riotboard \
    "


